---
title: Easy Spiced Pork Steak & Hollandaise with Mashed Potato & Steamed Greens
description: A hot contender for 'best new accompaniment', the ready-made Hollandaise in this dish really takes it to the next level. We're
serving it with mouth-watering spiced pork steaks, smooth mash and nourishing steamed greens.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
